 {
  "text": "I joined the hospital in 2004.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_i_joined_the_hospital_in_2004.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I started in the finance department.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_i_started_in_the_finance_department.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Then I became a business manager.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_then_i_became_a_business_manager.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "The network grew very fast.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_the_network_grew_very_fast.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Fernando, can I ask about your career? When did you start here?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_fernando_can_i_ask_about_your_career_when_did_yo.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Of course. I joined the hospital in 2004. I started in the finance department.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_of_course_i_joined_the_hospital_in_2004_i_starte.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Interesting! What was your first role?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_interesting_what_was_your_first_role.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I was a financial analyst. Then, after a few years, I became a manager.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_i_was_a_financial_analyst_then_after_a_few_years.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "A great journey. When did you move to oncology?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_a_great_journey_when_did_you_move_to_oncology.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "About ten years ago. Later, I grew the oncology network.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_about_ten_years_ago_later_i_grew_the_oncology_ne.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Amazing. So you have a lot of experience here.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_amazing_so_you_have_a_lot_of_experience_here.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Yes. Twenty-four years of experience, and a long career at one hospital.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_yes_twenty_four_years_of_experience_and_a_long_c.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "After a few years, I became a manager.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_after_a_few_years_i_became_a_manager.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "I have twenty-four years of experience.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_i_have_twenty_four_years_of_experience.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "My background is in finance and economics.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_my_background_is_in_finance_and_economics.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi, my name is Marcos, and I work with Fernando. Let me tell you about my career. I joined the hospital in 2008. I started as a junior analyst in the finance department. After three years, I got my first promotion. Then I became a project coordinator. Five years ago, I moved to the research team. Now I have a lot of experience in clinical projects. My background is in economics, like Fernando. It was a long journey, but a great one.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a2_listening_colleague.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hi Fernando, this is Sarah. I am preparing the agenda for our strategic meeting. I want to introduce you to our American partners. Can you send me a short summary of your career? Please tell me when you joined the hospital, your background, and your main promotions. Two or three lines are enough. Our partners want to know your experience in oncology. Thank you, and talk soon.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_listening_voicemail.mp3"
 },
